WEBVTT

00:03:27.211 --> 00:03:30.159
Rains all over the world.
What do you see?

00:03:30.159 --> 00:03:32.019
The equatorial region, in general,

00:03:32.019 --> 00:03:33.882
and the Amazon specifically,

00:03:33.882 --> 00:03:36.751
is extremely important
for the world's climate.

00:03:36.751 --> 00:03:38.916
It's a powerful engine.

00:03:38.916 --> 00:03:44.212
There is a frantic evaporation
taking place here.

00:03:44.212 --> 00:03:46.834
If we take a look at this other image,

00:03:46.834 --> 00:03:49.616
which shows the water vapor flow,

00:03:49.616 --> 00:03:52.801
you have dry air in black,
moist air in gray,

00:03:52.801 --> 00:03:54.232
and clouds in white.

00:03:54.232 --> 00:03:59.908
What you see there is an extraordinary
resurgence in the Amazon.

